title: 1 BR - Available Aug 1
posting_body: ['One bedroom apartment in Vailwood Apartment Community.', 'This is a beautiful apartment and we would love to show it to you,', "The Vailwood Community is located in a quiet, quaint valley in St. Paul's Eastern Heights neighborhood.", "It's a great location only 5 minutes to Woodbury and 5 minutes to Downtown St. Paul.", 'Interstate 94 and the MTC SunRay Transit Station are both only 3 blocks from our community.', "Shopping is easy at SunRay Shopping Center or you'll find several other stores within 1 mile of Vailwood such as: Target, TJ Maxx, 3 different grocers, several restaurants and retail stores--even the SunRay Library is nearby.", 'Parks surround the Vailwood Community like the following: Conway Park & Recreation, Mounds Park, Battle Creek Regional Park, Beaver Lake Park--Biking, Hiking, Swimming, Cross Country Skiing, Sledding, Softball, Basketball, Tennis--all are located just around the corner here at Vailwood.', "Shoot us an email or give us a call and we'll respond a.s.a.p."]
